# shellcheck config for this repo. See https://www.shellcheck.net/wiki/Directive
# for syntax. Disable per-file via `# shellcheck disable=SCxxxx` in the file.

# SC2015: `A && B || C` is not if-then-else. We use this idiom intentionally in
# trap-based cleanup blocks (`docker compose down ... || true`) where the goal
# is "best effort, never propagate failure."
disable=SC2015
